tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (
    user_id INT,
    dashboard_id INT,
    widget_id INT,
    widget_name VARCHAR(255),
    data_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE dashboard_widgets (
    widget_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    widget_name TEXT,
    widget_type TEXT,
    widget_data JSONB,
    dashboard_id INT REFERENCES data_visualization(dashboard_id)
);

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    activity_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE aggregation_logs (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    query_id INT,
    execution_time INT,
    result_count INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE query_history (
    query_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    query_text TEXT,
    execution_time INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_views (
    view_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    view_date DATE,
    view_time TIME,
    view_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    view_id INT,
    data_category VARCHAR(50),
    data_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_queries (
    query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    query_text TEXT,
    query_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    query_id INT,
    report_title VARCHAR(255),
    report_description TEXT,
    report_date DATE
)
